://www.nme.com/tag/harvey-weinstein">哈维·韦恩斯坦</a>提起诉讼，声称他在 1995 年对她进行了性侵犯。制片人否认了这一指控。</p><p>这位<em>《龙凤配》</em>的主演还向<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/disney">迪士尼</a>、米拉麦克斯和她的前经纪公司寻求赔偿，她说这些机构未能保护她免受虐待。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jury-finds-harvey-weinstein-guilty-of-rape-and-sexual-assault-during-los-angeles-trial-3369462">韦恩斯坦因强奸罪被判 23 年徒刑，目前正在服刑</a>。早在 20 世纪 70 年代末，已有 80 多人对制片人提出强奸和不当行为指控。</p><p>奥蒙德因在 90 年代电影<em>《战斗骑士》</em>和<em>《斯米拉的雪感</em>》中扮演的角色而闻名，她声称，在韦恩斯坦袭击后，她的事业再也没有恢复过来。</p><p>诉讼称，韦恩斯坦在一次商务晚宴后回到制片公司提供的公寓，在那里他“脱光衣服并强迫她为他进行口交”。</p><p> “如果米拉麦克斯或迪士尼对韦恩斯坦进行了适当的监督，并且在知道他对他在工作中遇到的女性构成危险的情况下不保留他，那么对奥蒙德的性侵犯本来是可以避免的，”提起的诉讼（来自<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-67013019"><em>BBC</em></a> ）说道。周三（10 月 4 日）。</p><p>韦恩斯坦的律师伊姆兰·安萨里告诉美联社，他的当事人“断然否认朱莉娅·奥蒙德对他的指控，他准备强烈为自己辩护”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3507704" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507704" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507704" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center.jpg" alt="哈维·韦恩斯坦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Harvey-Weinstein-appears-in-court-at-the-Clara-Shortridge-Foltz-Criminal-Justice-Center-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507704" class="wp-caption-text">哈维·韦恩斯坦。图片来源：盖蒂/艾蒂安·洛朗/泳池/法新社</figcaption></figure><p>奥蒙德还起诉了她以前的人才经纪公司创意艺术家经纪公司 (CAA)，她声称该经纪公司未能就韦恩斯坦的虐待行为向她发出警告。她还“表示，如果她向当局举报韦恩斯坦，他们不会相信她，而且他会严重损害她的职业生涯”。</p><p>诉讼还补充道：“更糟糕的是，在韦恩斯坦袭击奥蒙德并向他们报告袭击事件后不久，CAA 就失去了代表她的兴趣，她的职业生涯也遭受了巨大损失。</p><p>声明称：“韦恩斯坦的袭击及其后果对奥蒙德的职业生涯造成了灾难性的损害，无论是个人还是职业。”并补充说，由于被告涉嫌的袭击和报复，她“几乎从公众视野中消失”。</p><p>在奥蒙德的律师发表的一份声明中，这位英国演员表示：“几十年来，我一直对哈维·韦恩斯坦的经历充满痛苦的记忆，我对所有敢于发声的人感到谦卑和感激。”</p><p>她说，其他幸存者的“勇气”“揭示了像我在 CAA、米拉麦克斯和迪士尼的人才经纪人这样强大的人和机构是如何为韦恩斯坦攻击我和无数其他人提供掩护的”。</p><p> “我希望他们有责任承认自己所扮演的角色及其所造成的伤害的严重性，从而在一定程度上实现个人终结，并希望我们加深的理解将为我们所有工作人员提供进一步的保护。” </p><figure id="attachment_2369481" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2369481" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2369481" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032.jpg" alt="哈维·韦恩斯坦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/GettyImages-967633032-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2369481" class="wp-caption-text">哈维·韦恩斯坦。图片来源：法新社/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>该诉讼要求法院赔偿奥蒙德和奥蒙德的工资损失以及“精神痛苦和痛苦以及严重的情绪困扰”，金额不详。</p><p> CAA 表示，他们正在认真对待性侵犯指控，并对奥蒙德“抱有同情心”，但否认了针对该公司的指控。</p><p>该机构在一份声明中表示，“奥蒙德女士对 CAA 的指控毫无根据，该机构将在法庭上予以强烈反驳。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>还联系了迪士尼和米拉麦克斯征求意见。</p><p>今年 2 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harvey-weinstein-sentenced-to-16-additional-years-for-la-rape-conviction-3403990">韦恩斯坦被指控犯有另外三项强奸和性侵犯罪，并被追加 13 年监禁</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/julia-ormond-sues-harvey-weinstein-sexual-assault-3510068">演员朱莉娅·奥蒙德因性侵犯起诉哈维·韦恩斯坦和迪士尼的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Lady Gaga 胜诉 保留 50 万美元的绑架奖金https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-wins-case-to-keep-500000-dognapping-reward-3510061?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lady-gaga-wins-case-to- keep-500000-dognapping-rewardAnagricel Duran Thu, 05 Oct 2023 19:09:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3510061 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lady Gaga 于 2023 年 8 月 31 日在内华达州拉斯维加斯的米高梅公园举办“JAZZ &amp; PIANO”驻场演出。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为拉斯维加斯米高梅公园拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手此前曾被詹妮弗·麦克布赖德 (Jennifer McBride) 起诉，该女子被指控与 2021 年 Gaga 的两只狗被盗有关</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-wins-case-to-keep-500000-dognapping-reward-3510061">Lady Gaga 胜诉后要求保留 50 万美元的绑架奖励，该消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lady Gaga 于 2023 年 8 月 31 日在内华达州拉斯维加斯的米高梅公园举办“JAZZ &amp; PIANO”驻场演出。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为拉斯维加斯米高梅公园拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/lady-gaga-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>赢得了“找到”她的狗的女士对她提起的诉讼，并且不必支付承诺的 50 万美元（35.9 万英镑）的返还奖励。</p><p>詹妮弗·麦克布莱德 (Jennifer McBride) 因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gagas-dogwalker-shot-in-los-angeles-by-men-who-stole-two-of-her-bulldogs-2888941">2021 年流行歌手的两只法国斗牛犬被盗而</a>被指控，此前曾起诉 Gaga，要求获得奖金以及额外 150 万美元的损害赔偿。</p><p>周一（10 月 2 日），法官 Holly Fujie 做出了对 Gaga 有利的裁决，她（在<a href="https://people.com/lady-gaga-wins-temporary-victory-against-dog-thief-accomplice-500k-reward-lawsuit-7558948"><em>《人物》</em></a>杂志获得的法院命令中）表示，麦克布莱德在“参与盗窃”后，提出的申诉“在法律上不充分”。</p><p>法院命令还指出，麦克布莱德被起诉，并且对 2022 年接收被盗财产的指控没有提出异议，因此“此后无权通过寻求执行合同来从其不当行为中受益”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3510075" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510075" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510075" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga 于 2023 年 8 月 31 日在内华达州拉斯维加斯的米高梅公园举办“JAZZ &amp; PIANO”驻场演出。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为拉斯维加斯米高梅公园拍摄）" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1-1392x2088.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-performing-1-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510075" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga 于 2023 年 8 月 31 日在内华达州拉斯维加斯的米高梅公园举办“JAZZ &amp; PIANO”驻场演出。 （凯文·马祖尔/盖蒂图片社为拉斯维加斯米高梅公园拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> 2021 年 2 月，Gaga 的遛狗人 Ryan Fischer 在带着歌手的两只狗 Gustavo 和 Koji 外出散步时被枪杀。枪手在射杀费舍尔后偷走了他的狗。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gunman-who-shot-lady-gagas-dog-walker-has-been-sentenced-to-21-years-in-prison-3361028">詹姆斯·霍华德·杰克逊因枪杀费舍尔而被判处 21 年监禁</a>。他是袭击遛狗者的三名男子之一。</p><p>虽然这些人不知道这些狗是 Gaga 的，但他们知道它们很有价值。在菲舍尔拒绝交出狗后，杰克逊用手枪近距离射击了他， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gagas-dogwalker-had-part-of-his-lung-removed-after-shooting-recovery-isnt-a-straight-line-2910805">刺穿了他的肺部</a>并将他送往医院。</p><p>这位《Rain On Me》明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-calls-dogwalker-hero-breaks-silence-dog-theft-2890176" target="_blank" rel="noopener">于 2021 年 2 月 26 日首次公开谈论这起袭击事件</a>。 In two tweets, the star confirmed the $500,000 (£359k) reward that has been offered for the safe return of the dogs, adding: “If you bought or found them unknowingly, the reward is the same. I continue to love you Ryan Fischer, you risked your life to fight for our family. You&#39;re forever a hero.”</p><p> The two stolen dogs were returned unharmed by Ms McBride two days later after Gaga offered the reward. In April 2021, she was arrested on suspicion of acting as accessories to the theft and faced one count of receiving stolen property. </p><figure id="attachment_3510079" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510079" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510079" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga is seen out and about on June 22, 2015 in New York City. (Photo by Alessio Botticelli/GC Images)" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog-1392x2088.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Lady-Gaga-and-her-dog-1068x1602.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3510079" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga is seen out and about on June 22, 2015 in New York City. (Photo by Alessio Botticelli/GC Images)</figcaption></figure><p> In other news, Lady Gaga <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-dedicates-performance-of-born-this-way-to-victims-of-2017-las-vegas-shooting-3508197">dedicated a recent performance of &#39;Born This Way&#39; in Las Vegas to the victims of a mass shooting</a> that took place in the city in 2017.</p><p> The pop star was performing in at the Park MGM in Las Vegas on Sunday (October 1) when she played a stripped back version of her 2011 hit, pausing to pay tribute mid-way through the song.</p><p> “I just want to remind everyone here what a resilient wonderful city this is,” she said. “It has big hearts, and a lot of hope and believing in the future. And I just would like to dedicate this song to everyone we lost.”</p><p> She is currently<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-jazz-piano-las-vegas-residency-3475783">performing as part of her &#39;Jazz &amp; Piano&#39;</a> Las Vegas residency which she announced in July this year.</p><p> The &#39;Jazz &amp; Piano: The Las Vegas Residency&#39; is a celebration of her love of the Great American Songbook, featuring reworked versions of her biggest hits. Gaga first <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-plays-first-jazz-piano-show-las-vegas-full-setlist-2436219">launched her Jazz &amp; Piano show back in January of 2019</a> .</p><p> The announcement of the pop icon returning to stage came a week after <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tony-bennett-dies-aged-96-3471623">the death her longtime friend and collaborator, Tony Bennett</a> .</p><p> Gaga also recently featured on <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">The Rolling Stones</a> &#39; latest <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-share-lady-gaga-and-stevie-wonder-featuring-new-single-sweet-sounds-of-heaven-3506066">single &#39;Sweet Sounds Of Heaven&#39;</a> alongside <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">Stevie Wonder</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-wins-case-to-keep-500000-dognapping-reward-3510061">Lady Gaga wins case to keep $500,000 dognapping reward</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
